    <item>
      <title>华盛顿州土著马卡部落获准恢复捕鲸传统</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/13/nx-s1-5004700/indigenous-makah-tribe-in-washington-allowed-to-resume-whaling-tradition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国家海洋和大气管理局渔业部门周四决定给予华盛顿州马卡部落捕鲸豁免权，此后，华盛顿州马卡部落将可以恢复其长期捕鲸传统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/13/nx-s1-5004700/indigenous-makah-tribe-in-washington-allowed-to-resume-whaling-tradition</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 20:11:11 GMT</pubDate>
